data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Prepare to fall in love with this meticulously maintained property, offering the ideal canvas for your new beginning. Nestled in a vibrant community, this three-bedroom, two-bath home boasts sun-filled rooms, soaring ceilings, light fixtures with invisible fans, and access to a community pool - what's not to love? The heart of this home is the bright and open kitchen, complete with pristine white cabinetry, a generously sized center island with ample bar seating, and a stylish tile backsplash. It's an ideal space for the home chef in your life and those who love to entertain. Step into the adjoining living room with two-story ceilings, creating an airy and inviting atmosphere. A sliding door grants access to the 16 X 9 screened rear porch, where you can relax and enjoy the outdoors in comfort. A spiral staircase leads to the spacious loft upstairs, which offers the potential for a cozy reading room and a convenient office space, perfect for those who work from home or simply seek a quiet retreat. Beyond your doorstep, you'll discover a world of outdoor activities. Located nearby are the East Central Regional Rail Trail, Lake Monroe public boat ramp, and the St. Johns River, perfect for water enthusiasts. Green Springs and several parks offer opportunities for picnics and recreation, making this location a nature lover's paradise. Additional amenities include an attached garage, a five-year-old roof, and a formal dining room. Your new chapter starts in Deltona!
